    <!-- Detailed Services -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Listing Creation -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ“¸</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Listing Creation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                We create compelling listings on multiple platforms to maximize your exposure and bookings.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Professional Photography</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                High-quality photos are essential for attracting guests. Our professional photographers capture your unit's best angles, natural lighting, and key selling points. Photos are edited to pop on search results.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                * Additional one-time cost: RM500-1,000 (optional)
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Compelling Description</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We write descriptions that highlight Parkland Avenue's unique selling points: covered walkway to Jonker Street, 100+ facilities, oceanfront views, and more. Descriptions are optimized for Airbnb's search algorithm.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Dynamic Pricing Strategy</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We adjust rates based on demand, seasonality, and local events. This maximizes your occupancy while maintaining competitive pricing. We monitor competitor prices and market trends continuously.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700 mb-2">Multi-Platform Listing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We list your unit on Airbnb, Booking.com, Agoda, and other major platforms. This gives you maximum exposure to potential guests from around the world. All platforms are managed from one central dashboard.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Guest Communication -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ’¬</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Guest Communication</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Quick, professional responses are key to getting bookings. We handle all guest inquiries 24/7 so you never miss an opportunity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">24/7 Response Time</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We respond to all guest inquiries within minutes. Fast responses improve your listing's ranking in Airbnb search results and lead to more bookings. You never need to worry about checking messages.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Pre-Stay Information Packet</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Before arrival, we send guests detailed information about your unit, check-in process, parking, WiFi, and local recommendations. This reduces questions and improves guest experience.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">Check-in Coordination</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We coordinate all check-ins and check-outs smoothly. Whether you have a smart lock or key system, we ensure guests can access your unit without issues. We handle late arrivals and early check-ins.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-700 mb-2">During-Stay Support</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Guests can reach us 24/7 during their stay for questions, issues, or emergencies. We handle problems promptly so you can enjoy peace of mind.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cleaning & Maintenance -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 mb-6">
