                Professional cleaning and prompt maintenance keep your unit in top condition and lead to better reviews.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">Professional Cleaning</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                After every guest stay, we provide hotel-standard cleaning. This includes dusting, vacuuming, sanitizing bathrooms, kitchen cleaning, and fresh linens. Your unit is always guest-ready.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                * Frequency: After every guest checkout
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">Linen Management</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We provide and launder all bed linens, pillowcases, towels, and kitchen linens. Fresh, high-quality linens are essential for guest satisfaction and good reviews.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">Supply Replenishment</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                All essentials are restocked: toilet paper, soap, shampoo, dish soap, paper towels, and kitchen basics. You never need to shop or restock supplies.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-700 mb-2">Maintenance Coordination</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                If anything breaks or needs repair, we coordinate with trusted local contractors. We handle the scheduling, payment, and ensure quality work. You're kept informed throughout.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

