                Track your earnings effortlessly with our comprehensive financial management system.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-pink-700 mb-2">Monthly Income Reports</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                At the end of each month, receive a detailed income report showing: bookings, nights booked, income earned, expenses, and net income. Full transparency on your property performance.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-pink-700 mb-2">Automatic Payouts</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Your earnings are automatically deposited to your bank account each month. No chasing payments or dealing with platform disbursement issues. Timely, reliable payouts.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-pink-700 mb-2">Expense Tracking</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
